@startuml
autonumber

Actor User
Participant "Frontend (React)" as Frontend
Participant "Web API (Controllers)" as API
Participant "Business Logic (Services)" as BusinessLogic

User -> Frontend: Requests to download a file template (e.g., Excel import template)
Frontend -> API: GET /templates/{templateType}/download

alt Successful Template Retrieval
    API -> BusinessLogic: Call getTemplate service (templateType)
    BusinessLogic -> BusinessLogic: (Optional) Generate or retrieve specific template file content
    BusinessLogic --> API: Template file content (e.g., CSV, XLSX)
    API --> Frontend: Template file content (as file download)
    Frontend --> User: Initiates file download in browser
else Template Not Found or Error
    API --> Frontend: Error message (e.g., Template not found, Server error)
    Frontend --> User: Displays Error message
end

@enduml